DULL THUDS

55:31.160 --> 55:34.680
Argh!
PHONE RINGS

55:34.680 --> 55:37.040
DISTORTED ROARS

55:37.040 --> 55:39.320
SIREN SOUNDS

55:39.320 --> 55:40.960
Argh!

55:40.960 --> 55:42.920
SQUELCHING
THEY GRUNT

55:45.160 --> 55:47.120
LOUD THUD
Argh!

