55:50.440 --> 55:52.680
DULL THUDS

55:52.680 --> 55:55.160
METALLIC CLANG

55:57.320 --> 55:59.800
SQUELCHING
Argh!

56:08.000 --> 56:09.920
MUFFLED KNOCKING

56:09.920 --> 56:13.480
Mr Shelby. Is everything
all right in there?

56:16.200 --> 56:18.560
KNOCKING
Mr Shelby?

56:18.560 --> 56:20.040
Everything's fine.

56:21.280 --> 56:22.720
Everything's fine.

56:24.200 --> 56:26.840
PHONE RINGS

56:34.960 --> 56:36.880
Hello? Tommy.

56:36.880 --> 56:39.880
Tommy, she has a temperature
of 101 and nothing is working.

56:39.880 --> 56:42.400
Just get here now. Lizzie. Please.

56:42.400 --> 56:45.200
Lizzie.

56:45.200 --> 56:46.760
HE SIGHS

57:07.360 --> 57:10.200
Where is she?
She's with the doctor upstairs.

57:12.360 --> 57:14.400
Listen, Tommy.

57:14.400 --> 57:16.880
He said we shouldn't come close
to her, in case...

57:16.880 --> 57:18.880
In case of what?

57:18.880 --> 57:20.800
When she coughs, there's blood.

57:38.640 --> 57:40.760
Madonna,

57:40.760 --> 57:45.240
put me through to the number
I gave you for Esme Shelby Lee.

